  doneif (hero.tagcount[AbModify.cSoPElicEm] > 1)

  ~ Archetypes that replace emotions entirely are valid.
  validif (root.linkage[varies].tagcount[Helper.RemovePrim] = 0)]]></evalrule>
    </thing>
